{"id":586461,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/06/【网络民议】凭本事盗素材，华为这叫战狼精神啊/","date":"2018-06-09T07:59:42Z","modified":"2018-06-09T07:59:42Z","title":"【网络民议】凭本事盗素材，华为这叫战狼精神啊","content":"<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/1560906700/GkphKdDp6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@阑夕</a>：欧洲设计公司The Rusted Pixel用了14个月创造的作品被华为在发布会上盗用，尝试使用多种渠道联系都被无视，于是只好在Twitter上公开维权…… ​​​​</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pq6mobkj20gf0nednb.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-586462\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pq6mobkj20gf0nednb.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"570\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pq6mobkj20gf0nednb.jpg 591w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pq6mobkj20gf0nednb-211x300.jpg 211w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pq96fhmj21ao17lwj7.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-586463\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pq96fhmj21ao17lwj7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pq96fhmj21ao17lwj7.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pq96fhmj21ao17lwj7-300x280.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pqa5p64j21ao17lu0x.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-586464\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pqa5p64j21ao17lu0x.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pqa5p64j21ao17lu0x.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pqa5p64j21ao17lu0x-300x280.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pqae723j21ao17lq89.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-586465\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pqae723j21ao17lq89.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pqae723j21ao17lq89.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pqae723j21ao17lq89-300x280.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pqb0oevj21ao17ladd.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-586466\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pqb0oevj21ao17ladd.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"420\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pqb0oevj21ao17ladd.jpg 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/5d098bccly1fs3pqb0oevj21ao17ladd-300x280.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>以下评论由数字时代编辑收集自新浪微博：</strong></p>\n<p>@热心网友唐某某：华为一到店，所有喝茶的人便都看着它笑，有的叫道，“华为，你发布会又盗素材了！” 它不回答，对柜里说：“一份麒麟处理器，再来一份爵士三摄。”便排出几张单反拍的照片冒充手机照。他们又故意的高声嚷道，“你一定又想盗素材，要出个新手机了！” 华为睁大眼睛说，“你们怎么这样凭空污人清白……”</p>\n<p>@热心网友唐某某：“什么清白？我前天亲眼见你盗取国外广告公司的素材。”华为便涨红了脸，争辩道，“华为的事不能算盗取……爵士的事，能算盗取么？”接连便是难懂的话，什么“华为是爱国的”，什么“民族品牌”之类，引得众人都哄笑起来，店内外充满了快活的空气。</p>\n<blockquote><p>@王豚：图片评论</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/bae40809ly1fs3qins43bj20dc07zglo.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-586468\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/bae40809ly1fs3qins43bj20dc07zglo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"263\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/bae40809ly1fs3qins43bj20dc07zglo.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/bae40809ly1fs3qins43bj20dc07zglo-300x179.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/06/bae40809ly1fs3qins43bj20dc07zglo-80x48.jpg 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p></blockquote>\n<p>@让我问候你全家：每盗用一张图就可以省下一大笔授权费，资本主义就会损失一笔外汇，我国与资本主义国家的差距就会进一步缩小，菊花不愧是爱国企业，点赞了！</p>\n<p>@管鑫Sam:1，盗图可以甩锅给外包营销；2，被侵权的设计公司用所有可用方式联系交涉均被无视，这就是用不表态来表态了，态度明确的deafening silence；3，设计公司无奈在推上曝光求助… 好像在宇宙另一时空里，不知地球方向就乱比划SOS，谁知居然恰好有人穿过虫洞碰到了，史诗啊。</p>\n<p>@玲子汪汪:华为走国际化道路还敢这么来……</p>\n<p>@不瘦到130斤不改名惹:这叫战狼精神啊</p>\n<p>@Max士多啤梨：凭本事盗图，华为为祖国争光了</p>\n<p>@keely_姬:評論甩鍋廣告公司的算了吧，華為可是被英國廣告協會掛過牆頭經常比稿騙idea的惡劣甲方</p>\n<p>@告别文艺范：支持华为就是爱国，所以支持华为盗用</p>\n<p>@二七路：我国所谓的互联网公司创新主要靠VPN</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,17016],"tags":[18448,10268,33493,8646,9481,25822]}